//MainActivity Detail MAIN ACTIVITY PAGE This screen has three different categories namely list of songs based on artists,album name and all the songs. Mediaplayer class is used to play songs.
//Now Playing screen NOW PLAYING SCREEN This screen shows which song is being played and has play,pause and next and previous songs buttons.It uses the mediaplayerclass for audio controls.For the image depicting the album picasso library can be used.
//PlayList Screen This screen shows a list of songs based on the category selected on the main activity screen. It uses a ListView and custom array adapter
